.help_modal.modal
  %h2.header Where do I begin?
  %ul
    %li Drag an image from your desktop to the editor. It will be added to your sprites.
    %li Click on a sprite to add it to the current animation frame.
    %li Click the button to create a sequence.
    %li A sequences is a collection of one or more animation frames.
    %li Combine these sequences to create complex animation states.
